{"tid":1092411,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實男仔點先算關心一個女仔","createTime":"2019-04-04T21:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T21:33:14.000Z","uid":73533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0307f5176272763fd10bed6741c6c0fec3109e29","tid":1092411,"uid":73533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T21:16:18.000Z","msg":"前排因爲女朋友覺得我唔夠關心佢 差d散<br />\n雖然我都算哄番佢 但仲係緊緊於懷<br />\n我講下我背景先 岩岩畢左業出黎做野<br />\n但係女朋友仲讀緊書 準備畢業<br />\n有時因為咁 大家見面都小左<br />\n同埋有時我放左工都好攰 <br />\n搞到我有時搵小左佢<br />\n我認係我衰 但我仲係好愛你架女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果女朋友你睇到呢個post既話<br />\n真係好對唔住 但我會證明比你睇我係真係關心你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過都好想知道各位巴打或者絲打<br />\n通常會做d咩 令到另一半覺得對方關心自己<br />\n歡迎留言 大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb71fbe20de5b67281ce7e5d91a55cd9fcbc55f5","tid":1092411,"uid":32425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T21:18:20.000Z","msg":"當佢 post IG story 嘅事情<br />\n都無同你講<br />\n<br />\n咁你就咪死纏啦<br />\n<br />\n對方對你有感覺<br />\n自然會feel到<br />\n何必強求"},{"pid":"924b55e68e9e2650654e975491e28992ad997d87","tid":1092411,"uid":73533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb71fbe20de5b67281ce7e5d91a55cd9fcbc55f5","tid":1092411,"uid":32425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T21:18:20.000Z","msg":"當佢 post IG story 嘅事情<br />\n都無同你講<br />\n<br />\n咁你就咪死纏啦<br />\n<br />\n對方對你有感覺<br />\n自然會feel到<br />\n何必強求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T21:20:00.000Z","msg":"咁又冇你講到咁灰既 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fca97098db3027ac8e7c58073278467a6aad69","tid":1092411,"uid":32425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924b55e68e9e2650654e975491e28992ad997d87","tid":1092411,"uid":73533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb71fbe20de5b67281ce7e5d91a55cd9fcbc55f5","tid":1092411,"uid":32425,"like":1,"dislike":0